---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Terms of Service — Don't Lose Your Way" description="Terms of service for dontloseyourway.com.">
  <section class="legal-page"><div class="container legal-content">
    <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="legal-updated">Last updated: May 2026</p>
    <p>By using Don't Lose Your Way, you agree to these terms. If you disagree with any part, please do not use this platform.</p>
    <h2>What This Platform Is</h2>
    <p>Don't Lose Your Way is a digital storytelling and emotional support platform. It is not therapy, medical advice, or crisis intervention. It is a space for reflection, creative expression, and community connection.</p>
    <h2>Not a Substitute for Professional Help</h2>
    <p>This platform does not provide mental health services, diagnosis, or treatment. If you are in crisis or experiencing a mental health emergency, please contact the 988 Suicide & Crisis Lifeline immediately by calling or texting <strong>988</strong>.</p>
    <h2>User Content</h2>
    <p>When you share content (feelings, stories, lyrics) on this platform:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>You retain ownership of your content</li>
      <li>You grant us a limited license to display content you choose to share</li>
      <li>You can choose to keep submissions private or share them with the community</li>
      <li>We do not sell your content or personal information</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>AI-Generated Content</h2>
    <p>The Chapel feature uses AI to transform feelings into creative expression (lyrics, music). This AI-generated content is for personal reflection and creative expression only. It is not therapy, diagnosis, or professional advice.</p>
    <h2>Privacy</h2>
    <p>Our full <a href="/legal/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> explains how we handle your information. Key points:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>We collect minimal personal information</li>
      <li>Feelings shared privately are not stored long-term</li>
      <li>We use privacy-first analytics (no tracking cookies)</li>
      <li>We do not sell user data</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Age Requirement</h2>
    <p>This platform is intended for individuals 13 years of age and older. If you are under 13, please do not use this platform.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>For questions about these terms, please visit our <a href="/partners#contact">contact page</a>.</p>
    <p class="legal-crisis">If you are in crisis, please call or text <a href="tel:988"><strong>988</strong></a>.</p>
  </div></section>
</Layout>
<style>
  .legal-page { padding: 6rem 0; }
  .legal-content { max-width: 40rem; }
  .legal-content h1 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .legal-updated { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-text-subtle); margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .legal-content h2 { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 500; margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem; }
  .legal-content p { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; }
  .legal-content ul { margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem 1.5rem; }
  .legal-content li { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; line-height: 1.6; }
  .legal-content a { color: var(--color-accent); }
  .legal-crisis { background: rgba(239,68,68,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.3); border-radius: 0.5rem; padding: 1rem; text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem; }
  .legal-crisis a { color: var(--color-crisis); }
</style>